@startuml
title Deployment Sequence: Dash App on GCP App Engine

actor Developer
participant "Local Environment" as Local
participant "GCP CLI\n(gcloud)" as GCloud
participant "App Engine" as AppEngine
participant "Cloud Build" as CloudBuild
participant "Container Registry" as Registry
participant "VPC Network" as VPC
participant "BigQuery" as BQ
participant "Cloud Storage" as GCS

Developer -> Local: Configure app.yaml\n(service, project details)
activate Local
Local --> Developer: Configuration ready
deactivate Local

Developer -> Local: Update requirements.txt\n(dependencies)
activate Local
Local --> Developer: Dependencies specified
deactivate Local

Developer -> Local: Develop dash_app.py,\nload_data.py, create_charts.py
activate Local
Local --> Developer: Application code ready
deactivate Local

Developer -> Local: Test in Jupyter Notebook\n(test_plotly_charts.ipynb)
activate Local
Local --> Developer: Charts validated
deactivate Local

Developer -> GCloud: gcloud app deploy
activate GCloud
GCloud -> GCloud: Read app.yaml\nconfiguration

GCloud -> GCloud: Apply .gcloudignore\nfilters

GCloud -> CloudBuild: Initiate build process
activate CloudBuild

CloudBuild -> CloudBuild: Create container image\nfrom source code

CloudBuild -> CloudBuild: Install dependencies\nfrom requirements.txt

CloudBuild -> Registry: Push container image
activate Registry
Registry --> CloudBuild: Image stored
deactivate Registry

CloudBuild --> GCloud: Build complete
deactivate CloudBuild

GCloud -> AppEngine: Deploy application
activate AppEngine

AppEngine -> AppEngine: Configure flexible\nenvironment

AppEngine -> VPC: Connect to VPC network
activate VPC
VPC --> AppEngine: Network configured
deactivate VPC

AppEngine -> AppEngine: Start application\ncontainers

AppEngine -> AppEngine: Configure scaling\nand resources

AppEngine --> GCloud: Deployment successful
deactivate AppEngine

GCloud --> Developer: Deployment URL\n(app accessible)
deactivate GCloud

Developer -> AppEngine: Access deployed app\n(HTTP request)
activate AppEngine

AppEngine -> BQ: Load data\n(via load_data.py)
activate BQ
BQ --> AppEngine: Return data
deactivate BQ

AppEngine -> GCS: Load data\n(via load_data.py)
activate GCS
GCS --> AppEngine: Return data
deactivate GCS

AppEngine -> AppEngine: Create visualizations\n(create_charts.py)

AppEngine -> AppEngine: Render Dash UI\n(dash_app.py)

AppEngine --> Developer: Display interactive\nvisualization app
deactivate AppEngine

@enduml
